 "excerpt": "Circuit City is going the way of Linens 'n Things: 155 store closures were announced this morning. While we're keeping a few of our Circuit City stores in",
 "contentEncoded": "<p><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/11/circuitcity.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1226\" title=\"circuitcity\" src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/11/circuitcity.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"260\" height=\"260\"></a></p>\n<p>Circuit City is going the way of <a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/10/21/linens-n-things-one-persons-bankruptcy-is-anothers-treasure/\" target=\"_blank\">Linens &#x2018;n Things</a>: <a href=\"http://files.shareholder.com/downloads/CC/341737597x0x245809/2BFAC9D9-6CEF-4027-9E51-1C635F42F7A7/110308%20Store%20Closing%20List.pdf\" onclick=\"javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview(&apos;/outbound/article/files.shareholder.com&apos;);\" target=\"_blank\">155 store closures were announced this morning</a>. While we&#x2019;re <a href=\"http://www.circuitcity.com/ccd/processAddress.do#allStores\" onclick=\"javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview(&apos;/outbound/article/www.circuitcity.com&apos;);\" target=\"_blank\">keeping a few</a> of our Circuit City stores in Cool Springs, Madison and Bellevue, say goodbye to the stores at Hickory Hollow and in Spring Hill. Of course, what this means for us is that we can take our business to one of the liquidating stores and get some serious Christmas shopping done. Look for liquidation sales to start <a href=\"http://biz.yahoo.com/prnews/081103/nem065.html?.v=68\" onclick=\"javascript:pageTracker._trackPageview(&apos;/outbound/article/biz.yahoo.com&apos;);\" target=\"_blank\">Wednesday</a>.&#xA0;</p>\n\n\n\n\n<p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/01/16/for-real-this-time-bye-bye-circuit-city-comings-goings/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: (For Real This Time) Bye Bye, Circuit City [Comings &amp; Goings]\">(For Real This Time) Bye Bye, Circuit City [Comings &amp; Goings]</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/04/14/blockbusters-busted-white-bridge-store-shuts-doors-comings-goings/\" rel=\"bookma